sentences.en: Dell is exploring designs with different screen siz​es to its current 10-inch models, he said, though it was unclear if those new siz​es will be among the products released later this year. Dell is primarily interested in screen siz​es of 10 inches or larger, Lalla said.

Dell chủ yếu quan tâm đến kích cỡ màn hình 10 inch hoặc lớn hơn, ông Lalla nói.
